        <h2 class="cag-h2">Is This Timneh Breeder Legit — and How Would You Even Know?</h2>
        <p>The answer is that you check us out — and we go out of our way to make that painless, since the very tests that expose a scammer are the ones an honest breeder is glad to pass. C.A.Gs is a family aviary licensed under the USDA Animal Welfare Act, run by Mark &amp; Teri Benjamin here in Midland, Texas, with a license you can look up, breeding pairs we name out loud, and an open invitation to video-call you with Elad or Evie before a single dollar moves.</p>
