        <p>Plainly stated: we'll hop on a live call and put Elad or Evie on camera — hopping, chattering, closed band in view — before you part with anything. When a seller refuses that on a bird worth this much, take the hint; we would rather over-demonstrate than leave you second-guessing.</p>
