      <section id="shipping">
        <h2 class="cag-h2">How Does a Timneh African Grey Travel to You, and What's the Cost?</h2>
        <p>Timnehs go out on two straightforward tiers — $185 to the airport nearest you or $350 all the way to your door — and anyone inside a 2–3 hour drive of Midland we'll nudge toward a gentle in-person pickup instead. Each bird flies US-only on IATA live-animal cargo with its document folder aboard, and we lock in the carrier and the arrival window with you before it ever leaves the aviary.</p>
        <img class="sec-img inf-img" src={IMG + "timneh-african-grey-shipping-delivery.webp"} srcset={IMG + "timneh-african-grey-shipping-delivery-760.webp 760w, " + IMG + "timneh-african-grey-shipping-delivery.webp 1408w"} sizes="(max-width:860px) 92vw, 760px" width="1408" height="768" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="How a Timneh African Grey travels — IATA live-animal cargo and climate-controlled home delivery from Midland, Texas" />

        <h3 class="cag-h3">Which Delivery Option Fits You, and What Does Each Cost?</h3>
        <p>Pick whichever tier suits you: an airport pickup on Delta, United or American runs $185, while a climate-controlled home delivery is $350. Either way the health certificate and paperwork are already tucked in the folder, so homecoming day is spent settling your bird in rather than hunting for documents.</p>
        <div class="ship-cards">
          <div class="ship-c">
            <img src="/african-grey-airport-live-animal-shipping.webp" srcset="/african-grey-airport-live-animal-shipping-480.webp 480w, /african-grey-airport-live-animal-shipping.webp 640w" sizes="(max-width:900px) 92vw, 380px" width="640" height="797" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="Timneh African Grey traveling in an IATA-approved live-animal air cargo crate to the nearest airport" />
            <div class="ship-body"><span class="ship-tier">Tier 1</span><b>Airport Pickup</b><span class="ship-price">$185</span>
            <p>Your Timneh rides IATA live-animal cargo on Delta, United or American to the nearest major airport</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ship-c">
            <img src="/african-grey-home-delivery-pet-van.webp" width="640" height="426" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="Climate-controlled pet delivery van used for C.A.Gs Timneh African Grey home deliveries" />
            <div class="ship-body"><span class="ship-tier clay">Tier 2</span><b>Home Delivery</b><span class="ship-price">$350</span>
            <p>A climate-controlled pet courier brings your Timneh and its document folder straight to your doorstep</p></div>
          </div>
