          </div>
          <div class="otB-card feat">
            <span class="otB-name"><img src="/emoji/cag-timneh-64.webp" width="22" height="22" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async"> Timneh</span>
            <ul><li>9–11 in · 275–375 g</li><li>Maroon tail · horn beak</li><li>Early, clear talker · calmer-leaning</li><li>From $1,500</li></ul>
