      <!-- 15 · FAMILIES -->
      <section id="families">
        <h2 class="cag-h2">Which Families Have Bought a Documented Grey From Us?</h2>
        <p>Documented C.A.Gs greys now live with families in every corner of the country, and a couple of those families put it better than we can — each bought without meeting the bird first, and each saw the shipping and paperwork unfold exactly as promised here. You'll find dozens more first-hand accounts, photos included, on our <a href="/african-grey-reviews/">African Grey reviews</a> page.</p>
        <img class="sec-img og-photo" src={IMG + "happy-customer-timneh-african-grey.webp"} srcset={IMG + "happy-customer-timneh-african-grey-760.webp 760w, " + IMG + "happy-customer-timneh-african-grey.webp 1408w"} sizes="(max-width:860px) 92vw, 760px" width="1408" height="768" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="A C.A.Gs Timneh African Grey at home, socialized alongside the family's pet conure" />
