                <span class="stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">★★★★★</span>
              </div>
              <p>"{s.quote}"</p>
            </blockquote>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h3 class="cag-h3">Real Families, Real Papered Grey Parrots</h3>
        <p>The thread running through all of these stories is the exact paper trail your Timneh will carry — a DNA certificate, health records, CITES documentation — because a genuine outcome can only begin with a genuine, documented bird. We never invent a review, so whatever count you see here is the real one.</p>
