        <p>Ahead of a deposit, these reads dig further into the questions this page opens up — how to spot a scam, how to choose between a Congo and a Timneh, what your money actually buys, and the paperwork that makes a bird legal. Each was written here in our own aviary, not churned out by a content mill.</p>
