        <p>For care and ownership questions well past the point of sale, our full <a href="/african-grey-parrot-faq/">African Grey parrot FAQ</a> has you covered; what follows are the questions Timneh buyers actually email us — cost, legality, talking, temperament, lifespan and shipping — each answered the way we'd answer it if you called.</p>
